Howto install the new FreeRTOS BSP and the LwIP...?

This directory needs to be placed in the Demo directory of your FreeRTOS download. There you must run one of the following:

If you're on Windows execute alt-freertos-lwip-install.bat and if your on a unix like system execute alt-freertos-lwip-install.sh

Follow the instructions on the shell and you should be ready to go within a sec.

!!! Note !!!
The LwIP stack uses a modifed version of the socket API! If you want to update the LwIP version you should also apply this patch!
http://savannah.nongnu.org/patch/?7702

Instructions in FreeRTOS.readme.txt.

Enjoy!

